<Step 1> Goto EC2, Create the Security Groups with in bound NFS port enable
<Step 2> Goto EFS, Create the EFS with Networking assign the NFS enabled Security Groups
<Step 3> Goto ECS, Create Cluster
<Step 4> Goto ECS, Create Task (just like pod in K8s); Remove the port 80 (as not used in this docker image); Storage, Add volume,  
